.\}
.nf
$ mkvpropedit movie\&.mkv \-\-attachment\-name Arial\&.ttf \-\-attachment\-description \*(AqThe Arial font as a TrueType font\*(Aq \-\-attachment\-mime\-type application/x\-truetype\-font \-\-add\-attachment 89719823\&.ttf
.fi
